code: /**  * Same as {@link StreamNetworkThroughputBenchmark#setUp(int, int, int, boolean, int, int)}  * but also setups broadcast mode.  */ @Override public void setUp(int recordWriters, int channels, int flushTimeout, boolean localMode, int senderBufferPoolSize, int receiverBufferPoolSize) throws Exception {     setUp(recordWriters, channels, flushTimeout, true, localMode, senderBufferPoolSize, receiverBufferPoolSize, new Configuration()). }
